Images/Utility/Flags/medium/Vatican.gif
	" ALT="[Legamen ad versionem Latinam]"></A>
	<A CLASS="chapter" NAME="1.42">42</A>
The 8‑pipe: 2 digits in diameter; 6 digits plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">3</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">12</SPAN></SPAN> plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">10</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">288</SPAN></SPAN> in circumference; it has a capacity of 2 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN> plus ½ plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">1</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">24</SPAN></SPAN> plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">5</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">288</SPAN></SPAN>.

	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A HREF="
L/Roman/Texts/Frontinus/De_Aquis/text*.html#1.43
	"TARGET="Frontinus"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,LatinOriginal,WIDTH,180)"
onMouseOut="nd();"><IMG TITLE="" WIDTH="30" HEIGHT="20" SRC="
Images/Utility/Flags/medium/Vatican.gif
	" ALT="[Legamen ad versionem Latinam]"></A>
	<A CLASS="chapter" NAME="1.43">43</A>
The 10‑pipe: 2½ digits in diameter; 7 digits plus ½ plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">4</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">12</SPAN></SPAN> plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">7</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">288</SPAN></SPAN> in circumference; it has a capacity of 4 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN>.

	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A HREF="
L/Roman/Texts/Frontinus/De_Aquis/text*.html#1.44
	"TARGET="Frontinus"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,LatinOriginal,WIDTH,180)"
onMouseOut="nd();"><IMG TITLE="" WIDTH="30" HEIGHT="20" SRC="
