	" ALT="[Legamen ad versionem Latinam]"></A>
	<A CLASS="chapter" NAME="1.44">44</A>
The 12‑pipe: 3 digits in diameter; 9 digits plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">5</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">12</SPAN></SPAN> plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">3</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">288</SPAN></SPAN> in circumference; it has a capacity of 5 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN> plus ½ plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">3</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">12</SPAN></SPAN> plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">3</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">288</SPAN></SPAN>; is not in use.


<A ID="p381"><SPAN CLASS="pagenum"> p381 </SPAN></A>But with the water-men it measured 3 digits plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">1</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">24</SPAN></SPAN> plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">6</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">288</SPAN></SPAN> in diameter, containing 6 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN>.

	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A HREF="
L/Roman/Texts/Frontinus/De_Aquis/text*.html#1.45
	"TARGET="Frontinus"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,LatinOriginal,WIDTH,180)"
onMouseOut="nd();"><IMG TITLE="" WIDTH="30" HEIGHT="20" SRC="
Images/Utility/Flags/medium/Vatican.gif
	" ALT="[Legamen ad versionem Latinam]"></A>
	<A CLASS="chapter" NAME="1.45">45</A>
The 15‑pipe: 3 digits plus ½ plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">3</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">12</SPAN></SPAN> in diameter; 11 digits plus ½ plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">3</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">12</SPAN></SPAN> plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">10</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">288</SPAN></SPAN> in circumference; it has a capacity of 9 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN>.

	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A HREF="
L/Roman/Texts/Frontinus/De_Aquis/text*.html#1.46
	"TARGET="Frontinus"
