	" ALT="[Legamen ad versionem Latinam]"></A>
	<A CLASS="chapter" NAME="1.46">46</A>
The 20‑pipe: 5 digits plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">1</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">24</SPAN></SPAN> plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">1</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">288</SPAN></SPAN> in diameter; 15 digits plus ½ plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">4</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">12</SPAN></SPAN> plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">6</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">288</SPAN></SPAN> in circumference; it has a capacity of 16 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN> plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">3</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">12</SPAN></SPAN> plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">1</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">24</SPAN></SPAN>. With the water-men it measured 4 digits plus ½ in diameter, holding 13 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN>.

	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A HREF="
L/Roman/Texts/Frontinus/De_Aquis/text*.html#1.47
	"TARGET="Frontinus"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,LatinOriginal,WIDTH,180)"
onMouseOut="nd();"><IMG TITLE="" WIDTH="30" HEIGHT="20" SRC="
Images/Utility/Flags/medium/Vatican.gif
	" ALT="[Legamen ad versionem Latinam]"></A>
	<A CLASS="chapter" NAME="1.47">47</A>
The 25‑pipe: 5 digits plus ½ plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">1</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">12</SPAN></SPAN> plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">1</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">24</SPAN></SPAN> plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">5</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">288</SPAN></SPAN> in diameter; 17 digits plus ½ plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">2</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">12</SPAN></SPAN> plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">1</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">24</SPAN></SPAN> plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">7</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">288</SPAN></SPAN> in circumference; it has a capacity of 20 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN> plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">4</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">12</SPAN></SPAN> plus <SPAN CLASS="fraction"><SPAN CLASS="top">9</SPAN>&frasl;<SPAN CLASS="bottom">288</SPAN></SPAN>; is not in use.

	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A HREF="
L/Roman/Texts/Frontinus/De_Aquis/text*.html#1.48
	"TARGET="Frontinus"
