	<A CLASS="chapter" NAME="2.82">82</A>
Out of Tepula there were delivered outside the City in the name of Caesar 58 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN>, to private parties 56 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN>. The remaining 331 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN> were distributed within the City through the fourth, fifth, sixth, and seventh wards among fourteen reservoirs. Of these there were furnished in the name of Caesar 34 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN>, to private parties 237 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN>, for public uses 50 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN>, — namely, to one camp 12 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN>, to three public structures 7 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN>, to thirteen basins 32 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN>.

	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A HREF="
