Out of Julia there were flowed outside the City in the name of Caesar 85 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN>, to private parties 121 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN>. The remaining 548 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN> were distributed within the City to the second, third, fifth, sixth, eighth, tenth, and twelfth wards, among seventeen reservoirs. Of these there were furnished in the name of Caesar 18 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN>, to private parties 196 <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">quinariae</SPAN>,&#8203;<A CLASS="ref" ID="ref116" HREF="
