Praenomen not in <SPAN CLASS="manuscript">C</SPAN> but attested by <SPAN CLASS="small">CIL</SPAN> <SPAN CLASS="smaller">VI</SPAN>.2222, <SPAN CLASS="smaller">VIII</SPAN>.7066, <SPAN CLASS="smaller">IX</SPAN>.6083.78.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
