onMouseOut="nd();">2</A>
When it was necessary to carry the water pipes at a high elevation, the arched support was used in order to save 


<A ID="p333x"></A>masonry; otherwise a low foundation was built, to which the term <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">substructio</SPAN> is applied.


