"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">29</A>
125 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN> 


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note30" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Frontinus/De_Aquis/text*.html#ref30
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">30</A>
The country around <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">Tusculum</SPAN> (the modern <SPAN CLASS="modern">Frascati</SPAN>), a town in Latium <A CLASS="conversion"
onMouseOver="return Ebox('about 32 km',WIDTH,132)"
onMouseOut="nd();">•</A>about twenty miles south-east of Rome.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note31" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Frontinus/De_Aquis/text*.html#ref31
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">31</A>
Later it flowed in the same channel with Julia. <I>Cf.</I> <A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Frontinus/De_Aquis/text*.html#note35
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,5,WIDTH,140)"
onMouseOut="nd();">note on 9</A>.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note32" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Frontinus/De_Aquis/text*.html#ref32
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">32</A>
33 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN> 


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note33" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Frontinus/De_Aquis/text*.html#ref33
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
